Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: An unofficial C-API to the Last.fm web service
 libclastfm is an unofficial C-API for the Last.fm web service 
 written with libcurl. libclastfm supports much more than 
 basic scrobble submission. You can send shouts, fetch album covers 
 and much more. 
